        "text": "#2 Area of Activity: has shifted from far west to general areas of\nmidwest, central, south, and northwest. Indiana had 3 reports in 1\nday within a 100 mile area, or 4 reports in 7 days. Texas had 6 very\nimportant reports in 5 days, while the NY, N.J. and Pennsylvania area"
      },
